                                                            <td valign="top" class="mcnTextContent" style="padding: 0px 18px 9px;line-height: 125%;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;word-break: break-word;color: #202020;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;">

                                                                <div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:source sans pro,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif"><strong><span style="color:#333333"><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="line-height:41.6px">Thanks for signing up!</span></span>
                                                                    </span>
                                                                    </strong>
                                                                    </span><br> &nbsp;
                                                                </div>

                                                                <div style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family:source sans pro,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif">We know shipping sucks! </span><span style="font-family:source sans pro,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif">Airposted</span>
                                                                    <span
                                                                        style="font-family:source sans pro,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif">&nbsp;is a platform that connects buyers and travelers. We're really excited to see you here and look forward to building a trusted community that enables travelers&nbsp;to&nbsp;<strong>earn extra money</strong>&nbsp;while
                                                                        traveling<strong>&nbsp;</strong>and shoppers to&nbsp;<strong>shop for goods</strong>&nbsp;from anywhere in the world at the best prices.</span>
                                                                </div>

                                                                <div style="text-align: center;"><br>
                                                                    <span style="font-family:source sans pro,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#333333"><span style="font-size:15px">Here are a few ways we've made shipping more efficient:</span></span>
                                                                    </span><br> &nbsp;
                                                                </div>

                                                                <div style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family:source sans pro,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#333333"><span style="font-size:15px"><strong>Fast&nbsp;</strong>get items in as little as 48 hours.<br>
<br>
<strong>Affordable</strong> we don't step in and charge any fixed rates like traditional shipping. The traveler's carrying fee is completely negotiable between the buyer and traveler.<br>
<br>
<strong>Secure</strong>&nbsp;we hold the shopper's money in our escrow and&nbsp;release it to the traveler once they've made a successful delivery.<br>
<br>
<strong>Earn extra money&nbsp;</strong>travelers, earn money by carrying items on your trip.</span></span><br>
                                                                    <br>
                                                                    <strong><span style="font-size:15px">Shoppers</span></strong><span style="font-size:15px"><strong> get the best deals</strong> from anywhere in the world - delivered to them!</span></span>
                                                                </div>

                                                                <div style="text-align: left;"><br>
                                                                    <span style="font-family:source sans pro,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:15px"><span style="color:#333333">Note: Please complete your profile if you haven't already to accept offers and deals.</span></span>
                                                                    </span>
                                                                </div>

                                                                <div style="text-align: center;"><br>
                                                                    <span style="font-family:source sans pro,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:15px"><span style="color:#333333">Have questions? Check out our <a href="https://airposted.com/how-it-works" target="_blank" style="mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #ff7301;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: underline;">HOW IT WORKS</a> page or send us a message&nbsp;at </span>
                                                                    <a
